'''gbrainy'''是一个为[[GNOME|GNOME]]设计的[[智力游戏|智力游戏]]，属于[[教育软件|教育软件]]，旨在激发大脑潜力，授权协议是[[GNU通用公共许可证|GNU GPL]]。使用[[C_Sharp|C#]]编写，基于[[Mono|Mono]]<ref>{{cite web
 | url = http://wiki.laptop.org/go/GBrainy
 | title = GBrainy - OLPC
 | accessdate = 2010-04-19
 | language = en
 | archive-date = 2020-01-12
 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200112221943/http://wiki.laptop.org/go/GBrainy
 | dead-url = no
 }}</ref>并移植到[[Sugar_(用戶界面)|Sugar]]图形环境<ref>{{cite web
 | url = http://tirania.org/blog/archive/2008/Jan-03.html
 | title = Mono on the OLPC
 | first = Miguel
 | last = de Icaza
 | language = en
 | accessdate = 2009-10-25
 | archive-date = 2020-11-09
 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201109033609/https://tirania.org/blog/archive/2008/Jan-03.html
 | dead-url = no
 }}</ref>以及[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]。

主要包含：
* 逻辑游戏：考验思考分析能力。
* 计算：心算锻炼。
* 记忆：锻炼短时记忆。

